T02D2333:276a-1: panytsa kra ma sam gra ha pra bha wa /
T02D2333:276a-3: rim pa lnga bsdus pa gsal ba /
T02D2333:276a-4: dpal ldan bla ma'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2333:276a-5: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba che //
T02D2333:276a-6: rim pa lnga la gnas pa po //
T02D2333:276b-0: dngos @276b po'i gnas lugs lam dang ni //
T02D2333:276b-2: dngos po gnas lugs gnyis yin te //
T02D2333:276b-3: sems dang lus kyi gnas thabs las //
T02D2333:276b-4: rags dang phra dang shin tu phra //
T02D2333:276b-5: thun mong dbyer med rim zhes bya //
T02D2333:276b-6: gnyid dang rmi lam snyoms 'jug pa //
T02D2333:276b-7: tha mal dus dang rnam pa bzhi //
T02D2333:276b-8: 'khor lo bzhi yi bdag nyid kyis //
T02D2333:276b-9: rtsa dang thig le sems shes pa //
T02D2333:276b-10: lus dang dus dang yul gyi ni //
T02D2333:276b-11: gnad ni bzhi ru shes par bya //
T02D2333:276b-12: dran pa sna chogs rnam rtog rnams //
T02D2333:276b-13: sems las yang dag 'byung bas na //
T02D2333:276b-14: rnam shes srog ni 'du ba'i rten //
T02D2333:276b-15: snying gar sngags kyi dkyil 'khor lo bsgom //
T02D2333:276b-16: gzhi lam 'bras bu rab shes pas //
T02D2333:276b-17: lus dben sngags dang sems gsum gyi //
T02D2333:276b-18: sgyu ma mngon par byang chub pa //
T02D2333:276b-20: sngags kyi yi ge'i 'khor lo ni //
T02D2333:276b-21: dang por chu skyes 'dab brgyad pa //
T02D2333:276b-22: phyi nang gsang ba'i tshul gyis ni //
T02D2333:276b-23: rim pa ldan par bsam gtan bya //
T02D2333:276b-24: phyi rim shes rab dbyangs yig mtshan //
T02D2333:276b-25: bar ma gsal byed thabs bcas pa //
T02D2333:276b-26: gnyis su med par nang mar gnas //
T02D2333:276b-27: phyogs mtshams rim par ting nge 'dzin //
T02D2333:276b-28: sbyor ba rnam pa gsum rang bzhin //
T02D2333:276b-29: dbus su mig gi thig le ste //
T02D2333:276b-30: aa dang bcas pa srog gyur gang //
T02D2333:276b-31: gun gyi snying po spro zhing sdud //
T02D2333:276b-32: 'byung ba bzhi yi rlung rnams nyid //
T02D2333:276b-33: rlung dang sngags su rab sbyor bas //
T02D2333:276b-34: rdo rje bzlas pa sbyang bar bya //
T02D2333:276b-36: tha mal rnam rtog bag chags rnams //
T02D2333:276b-37: sngags nyid sems su dmigs pas so //
T02D2333:276b-38: lus dag pas ni rtog pa dag / rlung dag pas ni dri med 'gyur //
T02D2333:276b-39: rlung dag pas ni ye shes kyi //
T02D2333:276b-40: kun rdzob sgyu ma mngon du byed //
T02D2333:276b-41: de nyid mngon par byang chub pas //
T02D2333:276b-43: las rnams bya ba phrin las tshogs //
T02D2333:276b-44: rnam shes ye shes sbyor bas 'grub //
T02D2333:276b-45: rtags rnams rim par 'char ba'i dngos //
T02D2333:276b-46: ye shes lnga yi rgyu mthun nyams //
T02D2333:276b-48: yan lag rlung las mngon shes 'thob //
T02D2333:276b-49: rtog pa'i tshogs ni mar 'grib cing //
T02D2333:277a-2: ye shes rim pa rang las rnyed //
T02D2333:277a-3: gcig dang du mar dmigs mi phyed //
T02D2333:277a-4: dang po smig rgyu lta bu'i nyams //
T02D2333:277a-6: gnyis pa zla ba lta bu dang //
T02D2333:277a-8: mtshams snang las ni thob pa ste //
T02D2333:277a-9: mtshams bral dus kyi ye shes che //
T02D2333:277a-10: mngon par byang chub tshul gnas pas //
T02D2333:277a-11: dri med ye shes mngon par rdzogs //
T02D2333:277a-12: rtags dang rtags can 'char tshul ni //
T02D2333:277a-13: ye shes 'bar dang rdzogs pa'i dus //
T02D2333:277a-14: rlung sems tsam las 'byung ba yi //
T02D2333:277a-15: sgyu ma'i lus ni snang bar bcas //
T02D2333:277a-16: 'od gsal rgyun gyi bsam gtan gyis //
T02D2333:277a-17: las dang sgrib pa bag chags sbyangs //
T02D2333:277a-18: sa lam rtags kyi rim pa'i tshogs //
T02D2333:277a-20: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor dbus gnas par //
T02D2333:277a-21: gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam par bya //
T02D2333:277a-22: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i sa bon la //
T02D2333:277a-23: dbus su srog gi sa bon te //
T02D2333:277a-24: yi ge ka nas ha yig bar //
T02D2333:277a-25: ksha ni spangs pa'i gzhi bcas pa //
T02D2333:277a-26: dbyangs ni phyi rim snang ba ste //
T02D2333:277a-27: gsal byed bar ma mched pa nyid //
T02D2333:277a-28: ma ning snang ba thob par brjod //
T02D2333:277a-29: bcu gnyis yi ge thig ler bcas //
T02D2333:277a-30: phreng ba lta bur gnas pa ni //
T02D2333:277a-31: rim pa lnga ldan bsam par bya //
T02D2333:277a-33: ae wam thabs dang shes rab las //
T02D2333:277a-34: sdud cing spro bar mdzad pa yi //
T02D2333:277a-35: aa zhes dbus su gnas par mdzad //
T02D2333:277a-36: mnyam pa nyid du sems bsdam ste //
T02D2333:277a-37: mnyam gzhag 'khor lo'i lte ba yis //
T02D2333:277a-38: ye shes mnyam par mthong gyur pa //
T02D2333:277a-39: nye bar thob pa stong pa che //
T02D2333:277a-40: 'od gsal ba yi gnas thob pa //
T02D2333:277a-42: thun gcig yang ni nyin gcig gam //
T02D2333:277a-43: zla phyed zla ba lo yi dus//
T02D2333:277a-44: bskal pa'am bskal pa stong du yang //
T02D2333:277a-45: skad cig re rer gnas pa ni //
T02D2333:277a-46: ye shes sbyor ba rtag tu 'byung //
T02D2333:277a-47: rim pa gnyis pa la gnyis pa //
T02D2333:277a-48: mnyam par zung 'brel nyid bsgom pa //
T02D2333:277a-49: bskyed pa'i rim 'di lha yi sku //
T02D2333:277b-0: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor mchog / rnam pa @277b mngon du byed pa gang //
T02D2333:277b-1: legs par bslabs pas mthar phyin 'gyur //
T02D2333:277b-2: lus dben snang ba sems dang lus //
T02D2333:277b-3: rgyu dang mi rgyu 'jig rten bcas //
T02D2333:277b-4: rim pas lha yi bdag nyid sbyor //
T02D2333:277b-5: rdo rje 'chang chen lam du byed //
T02D2333:277b-6: mos pa las byung ting nge 'dzin //
T02D2333:277b-9: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las //
T02D2333:277b-10: rlung sngags mnyam par rab sbyor gang //
T02D2333:277b-11: rdo rje bzlas pa'i rim pa'o //
T02D2333:277b-12: gsang sngags las byung rnam par shes //
T02D2333:277b-13: snang ba gsum gyi bdag nyid ni //
T02D2333:277b-14: ye shes 'jug ldog nges pa gang//
T02D2333:277b-15: sems la dmigs pa'i rim pa'o //
T02D2333:277b-16: rmi lam lus ni rnam sbyangs phyir //
T02D2333:277b-17: sgyu mar mtshon pa'i dus gang las //
T02D2333:277b-18: yul snang kun rdzob gang byung ba //
T02D2333:277b-19: sgyu ma lta bu'i rim pa'o //
T02D2333:277b-20: rang bzhin shes pa bsam gtan las //
T02D2333:277b-21: thabs las ma bskyed ting nge 'dzin //
T02D2333:277b-22: rang gsal ngo bo mi rtog pa //
T02D2333:277b-24: bsam gtan mes sbyangs lha yi sku //
T02D2333:277b-25: rang byung ye shes dag pa'i lus //
T02D2333:277b-26: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed bral bar gnas //
T02D2333:277b-28: byang chub sems ldan bla ma dang //
T02D2333:277b-29: lhag pa'i lha yi rnal 'byor dang //
T02D2333:277b-31: rjes su rnal 'byor bcas pa dag / ting 'dzin rim pa ldan pa yis //
T02D2333:277b-32: bsnyen pa nyer sgrub sgrub pa che //
T02D2333:277b-33: sgrub pa'i ngo bo khyad par du //
T02D2333:277b-34: so sor sdud dang bsam gtan dang //
T02D2333:277b-35: srog rtsol de bzhin 'dzin pa dang //
T02D2333:277b-36: rjes su dran dang ting nge 'dzin //
T02D2333:277b-37: yan lag drug ldan khyad par ro //
T02D2333:277b-38: rim pa bzhi ldan phyag rgyar bcas //
T02D2333:277b-39: dbang bzhi sku bzhi rang 'byung bas //
T02D2333:277b-40: mngon par byang chub tshul lnga las //
T02D2333:277b-41: bskyed dang bskyed cing gnas pa dang //
T02D2333:277b-42: lam gyur rim pa lnga ldan pas //
T02D2333:277b-43: byang chub phyogs chos mdo don dang //
T02D2333:277b-44: spras pa rnam gsum mthar thug bcas //
T02D2333:277b-45: sna tshogs sgra ni mtshon pa'o //
T02D2333:277b-46: gtum mo'i rnal 'byor rlung gis te //
T02D2333:277b-47: bde chen sems la dmigs pa'o //
T02D2333:277b-48: rmi lam sgyu ma gcig tu sbyangs //
T02D2333:277b-49: bar do rnam gsum bsre ba nyid //
T02D2333:277b-50: nyon mongs ye shes lam du 'gyur //
T02D2333:278a-2: grong du 'jug pa yan lag go //
T02D2333:278a-3: 'od gsal gnas thob mngon sangs rgyas //
T02D2333:278a-5: le lo can ni 'chi kha ste //
T02D2333:278a-6: tha ma srid pa'i bar ma ngor //
T02D2333:278a-7: mchog thob skus ni gzhan don byed //
T02D2333:278a-8: ngo bo rgyu tshul 'byung ba khams //
T02D2333:278a-9: las dang ngo bo dbye ba de nyid rlung //
T02D2333:278a-11: 'bru gsum sngags kyi ngo bo nyid //
T02D2333:278a-12: a'a li k'a li sbyor dbus las //
T02D2333:278a-13: brtags pa grangs ldan bzlas pa nyid //
T02D2333:278a-14: sbyor dang khyad par thabs ldan pas //
T02D2333:278a-15: ngag dben rlung gi rnal 'byor bstan //
T02D2333:278a-16: rgyu dang 'bras bu sbyor ba gang //
T02D2333:278a-17: snang ba gsum gyi 'char tshul te //
T02D2333:278a-19: dbyer med ye shes gnas thob pa //
T02D2333:278a-20: spyod pa ye shes mngon du byed //
T02D2333:278a-21: slob dang mi slob der spyod pa'o //
T02D2333:278a-22: rang bzhin shes pa'i lam gyur pa //
T02D2333:278a-23: rnam shes sgyu mar mtshon pa'i chos //
T02D2333:278a-24: khyad par las dang spyod pa dang //
T02D2333:278a-25: dngos grub thob phyir bdag byin rlabs //
T02D2333:278a-26: phyi nang mngon par byang chub tshul //
T02D2333:278a-27: rnal 'byor thob pas bsam gtan gnas //
T02D2333:278a-29: spyod tshul ye shes de thob po //
T02D2333:278a-30: lta dang nyams myong lus dang ngag / bsam gtan mnyam rjes spyod pa dang //
T02D2333:278a-31: slob dang mi slob gnyis med cing //
T02D2333:278a-32: rab tu mi gnas zung du 'jug / yi ge'i don dang spyi yi don //
T02D2333:278a-33: sbas dang mthar thug nyid yin te //
T02D2333:278a-34: theg pa sna tshogs pha rol phyin //
T02D2333:278a-35: srid par skye dang gnas la sogs //
T02D2333:278a-36: dus kyi dbye ba'i khyad par gyi //
T02D2333:278a-37: stan gcig steng du bsgom par bya //
T02D2333:278a-39: lam mchog rim pa lnga po nyid //
T02D2333:278a-40: pha rol phyin dang theg sna tshogs //
T02D2333:278a-41: srid pa skye dang nyin zhag gcig / stan gcig steng du sbyar te bshad //
T02D2333:278a-42: 'bras bu skye ba'i rim pa nyid //
T02D2333:278a-43: tshe 'di nyid du sangs rgyas te //
T02D2333:278a-44: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dam pa ste //
T02D2333:278a-45: sku lnga rab rdzogs gyur pa'o //
T02D2333:278a-46: rim pa lnga'i don bsdus pa gsal ba zhes bya
T02D2333:278a-47: ba dpal ldan n'a ro pas mdzad pa'i gsang ba'i
T02D2333:278a-48: man ngag bla ma'i zhal las rtogs par bya ba
T02D2333:278a-51: bod kyi lo ts'a ba mar pa chos kyi blo
T02D2333:278a-52: gros kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa
T02D2333:278a-53: / 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi bstan pa
T02D2333:278a-54: phyogs dus thams cad du dar zhing rgyas par gyur
